research/history/round_summaries/round_0229.json:19:    "hypothesis": "\u5019\u9009 family \u8bbe\u4e3a `lowrank_expert_residual`\u3002\u6700\u7ec8\u91cd\u6784\u516c\u5f0f\u4e3a `x_hat = \u03a3_r \u03b2_r(x) u_r + \u03a3_{i\u2208S_{e(x)}(x)} \u03b1_{e,i}(x) b_{e,i} + \u03a3_j \u03b3_j(x) c_j`\uff0c\u5176\u4e2d `U={u_r}` \u662f\u9759\u6001 low-rank trunk \u5411\u91cf\u5e93\uff0c`{B_e}` \u662f routed expert \u9759\u6001\u5b50\u5e93\uff0c`C={c_j}` \u662f\u5168\u5c40 residual \u9759\u6001\u8865\u507f\u5e93\u3002\u5728\u7ebf\u5bfc\u51fa\u94fe\u8def\u4ecd\u662f\u201ctrunk \u67e5\u8868 + routed expert \u5b50\u5e93\u67e5\u8868 + residual \u8865\u507f\u67e5\u8868 + \u6709\u9650\u52a0\u6743\u548c + \u9009\u62e9\u6027\u5728\u7ebf\u8865\u507f\u201d\uff0c\u9759\u6001\u5e93\u4e0d\u968f\u6837\u672c\u52a8\u6001\u751f\u6210\uff0c\u56e0\u6b64\u8be5 family \u5224\u5b9a\u4e3a `\u6269\u5c55\u517c\u5bb9`\u3002`expert_topk`\u3001`shared_routed_expert_topk`\u3001`lowrank_expert_topk` \u7b49\u4ecd\u5c5e\u517c\u5bb9 family\uff1b`batch_topk`\u3001`adaptive_budget_topk` \u7b49 batch/sample-coupled family \u4ecd\u5c5e `\u4e0d\u517c\u5bb9`\uff0c\u4e0d\u80fd\u9a71\u52a8\u5f53\u524d objective leaderboard\u3002\u672c\u8f6e\u552f\u4e00\u4e3b\u5047\u8bbe\u662f\uff1aRound 220 \u4e4b\u540e\uff0c\u4f4e\u6210\u672c selector / factorized / single-library \u7ebf\u5df2\u7ecf\u88ab\u8fde\u7eed\u8d1f\u4fe1\u53f7\u57fa\u672c\u88c1\u5c3d\uff0c\u4f46\u5f53\u524d\u9ad8\u4f18\u5148\u7ea7\u91cc\u4ecd\u6709\u4e00\u4e2a\u5c1a\u672a\u5728 `r212` exact recipe \u4e0a\u5e72\u51c0\u88c1\u51b3\u7684\u6838\u5fc3\u7ed3\u6784\u95ee\u9898\uff0c\u5373\u201cshared low-rank trunk + routed residual experts\u201d\u672c\u8eab\u662f\u5426\u503c\u5f97\u7ee7\u7eed\u3002\u56e0\u800c\u76f8\u5bf9 r212 \u4ec5\u628a `ARCHITECTURE` \u4ece `expert_topk` \u5207\u5230 `lowrank_expert_residual`\uff0c\u4fdd\u6301 `K=32`\u3001`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`\u3001`OPTIMIZER=adam`\u3001`LR=8e-4` \u4e0e\u5176\u4f59\u4e3b recipe \u4e0d\u53d8\uff0c\u76f4\u63a5\u6d4b\u8bd5\u6781\u77ed sparse path \u4e0b\u52a0\u5165 low-rank trunk \u4e0e residual cleanup \u540e\uff0c\u662f\u5426\u4f1a\u51fa\u73b0\u8db3\u591f\u5927\u7684 exceed \u5d29\u584c\uff0c\u4ece\u800c\u8bc1\u660e\u8be5\u7ed3\u6784\u7ebf\u4ecd\u503c\u5f97\u540e\u7eed\u7528 `TRUNK_RANK` / `STAGE1_RATIO` / `K` \u53bb\u538b\u7f29\u3002\u672c\u5730\u7cbe\u786e\u6210\u672c\u590d\u6838\u663e\u793a\u8be5\u70b9 selection_accesses=1605632\u3001deployment_accesses=245760\u3001combined_accesses=1851392\uff0c\u5bf9\u5f53\u524d 1024x4096 fused-QKV proxy \u7684 exact total_cost_ratio=0.44140625\uff1b\u82e5\u8981\u5237\u65b0 r212 \u7684 objective=0.35553750753402713\uff0c\u9700\u8981 exceed_alpha_0.50 \u538b\u5230\u7ea6 `\u2264-0.08586874246597288`\uff0c\u8fd9\u5728\u6570\u5b66\u4e0a\u5df2\u4e0d\u73b0\u5b9e\u3002\u56e0\u6b64\u8fd9\u4e0d\u662f\u4e00\u4e2a\u8fd1\u7aef\u7ffb\u76d8\u70b9\uff0c\u800c\u662f\u4e00\u8f6e\u9ad8\u98ce\u9669\u4f46\u9ad8\u4fe1\u606f\u589e\u91cf\u7684 architecture-slot verdict\uff1a\u5982\u679c\u5b83\u8fde\u5728\u5f53\u524d anchor recipe \u4e0b\u90fd\u4e0d\u80fd\u663e\u8457\u538b\u4f4e exceed\uff0c\u90a3\u4e48\u8fd9\u6761 trunk+expert+residual \u4e3b\u5f20\u5728\u5f53\u524d hookpoint \u4e0a\u5e94\u6574\u4f53\u964d\u7ea7\u3002",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0229.json:37:      "\u5f53\u524d remaining high-priority yet unclosed \u7684\u7ed3\u6784\u69fd\u4f4d\u91cc\uff0c`lowrank_expert_residual` \u6bd4 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_residual` \u548c `shared_routed_factorized_expert_residual` \u66f4\u8d34\u8fd1\u7528\u6237\u660e\u786e\u70b9\u540d\u7684 trunk + routed residual expert \u65b9\u5411\uff0c\u4e14\u65e7\u5386\u53f2\u91cc\u4e5f\u66fe\u7ed9\u51fa\u66f4\u4f4e exceed \u7684\u5f31\u5148\u9a8c\u3002",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0134.json:7:  "family_name": "shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0134.json:19:    "hypothesis": "最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = Σ_{i∈S_sh(h(x))} α_i^sh(x) u_i + Σ_{e∈E(h(x))} Σ_{j∈S_e(x)} α_{e,j}(x) b_{e,j}，其中 h(x)=Bx 是共享低秩投影，U={u_i} 是静态 shared library，{B_e} 是静态 routed expert 子库。在线侧仍可导出为“shared low-rank projection + shared library lookup + routed expert local top-k + 有限加权和”，静态库不随样本动态生成，因此 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk` 判定为直接兼容；`batch_topk`、`adaptive_budget_topk` 等 batch/sample-coupled family 仍属不兼容，不能驱动 frontier。唯一主假设：相对 r129 仅把 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM` 从 256 降到 192，在保持 `K=128`、`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`、`NUM_EXPERTS=64`、`ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2`、`LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=320` 与其余训练配方不变时，shared low-rank basis 仍能覆盖主要全局结构，而更窄的 shared scorer 不会显著伤害 routed expert 质量，从而把总成本从约 0.37x 压到约 0.35x，并直接回答当前最优先的 hetero MoE 线是否能通过进一步低秩化进入新的低成本结构前沿。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0134.json:20:    "summary": "Round 134 建议回到当前最值得补信息的 hetero MoE 线，而不是继续在最近连续失败的 family 上切新架构。以 r129 为 reference，只改 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=192`，用一次 matched-cost 压缩直接测试 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk` 是否能通过更窄 shared scorer 形成新的低成本结构锚点。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0134.json:23:    "family_name": "shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0134.json:25:    "self_review": "满足单轮单变量约束：相对 r129 只改 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM`。这轮不是回到 `shared_routed_expert_topk` 或 `lowrank_expert_*` 做旧 family 局部扫参，而是沿当前最有结构信息价值的 hetero MoE 原型 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk` 做一次定向低秩压缩，直接回应 prompt 对“shared low-rank basis + expert-specific head / local top-k”方向的优先级。主要风险是该 family 在 r129 已接近但未进入 frontier，192 可能仍被现有 0.32x-0.37x 点支配；但这是当前最清晰的一次单变量结构压缩对照。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0134.json:35:      "本地 allowlist 校验已通过：`shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk` 允许 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM` param-only override。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0134.json:36:      "本地 smoke 已通过：`ARCHITECTURE=shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk, K=128, EF=1, FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=192, NUM_EXPERTS=64, ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2, LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=320` 可 instantiate/forward/backward。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0134.json:53:    "architecture": "shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0134.json:62:    "description": "Round 134 建议回到当前最值得补信息的 hetero MoE 线，而不是继续在最近连续失败的 family 上切新架构。以 r129 为 reference，只改 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=192`，用一次 matched-cost 压缩直接测试 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk` 是否能通过更窄 shared scorer 形成新的低成本结构锚点。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0134.json:63:    "self_review": "满足单轮单变量约束：相对 r129 只改 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM`。这轮不是回到 `shared_routed_expert_topk` 或 `lowrank_expert_*` 做旧 family 局部扫参，而是沿当前最有结构信息价值的 hetero MoE 原型 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk` 做一次定向低秩压缩，直接回应 prompt 对“shared low-rank basis + expert-specific head / local top-k”方向的优先级。主要风险是该 family 在 r129 已接近但未进入 frontier，192 可能仍被现有 0.32x-0.37x 点支配；但这是当前最清晰的一次单变量结构压缩对照。",
