research/history/round_summaries/round_0129.json:19:    "hypothesis": "最终重构公式为 x_hat = Σ_{i∈S_sh(h(x))} α_i^sh(x) u_i + Σ_{e∈E(h(x))} Σ_{j∈S_e(x)} α_{e,j}(x) b_{e,j}，其中 h(x)=Bx 是共享低秩投影，U={u_i} 是静态 shared library，{B_e} 是静态 routed expert 子库。在线侧可导出为“shared low-rank projection + shared library lookup + routed expert local top-k + 有限加权和”，静态库不随样本动态生成，因此 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk` 判定为直接兼容；`batch_topk`、`adaptive_budget_topk` 仍是不兼容 family，不能驱动 frontier。唯一主假设：相对 r128 仅把 `ARCHITECTURE` 从 `shared_routed_factorized_expert_topk` 切到已实际落盘的新 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk`，保持 `K=128`、`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`、`FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=256`、`NUM_EXPERTS=64`、`ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2`、`LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=320` 与其余训练配方不变，直接回答 r127-r128 的负信号是否主要来自“routed experts 也被一并 factorize”这一结构限制；如果是，则新 family 应在 fresh cost 约 selection=0.24x、deployment=0.12x、total=0.37x 的低成本带显著优于 0.2248，并决定这条 shared-lowrank + full-routed-head 结构是否值得继续扩展。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0129.json:20:    "summary": "已实际落盘新 family `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk`：shared 分支保留低秩 scorer，routed experts 改回 full-dim local heads，用来做对 r127-r128 的最小结构修正。建议本轮以 r128 为 reference，只改 `ARCHITECTURE=shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk`，用同配方直接判断当前 shared+routed 负信号是否主要来自过度 factorize routed experts。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0129.json:23:    "family_name": "shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0129.json:25:    "self_review": "满足单轮单变量约束：计划运行时相对 r128 只改 `ARCHITECTURE`。这轮不是回到旧 family 的局部扫参，而是落一个最小新原型，直接隔离“shared+routed 失败是否来自把 routed heads 也 factorize”这个高信息量结构问题。按 `sae-architecture-integration` 检查，whitelist、factory dispatch、具体类实现和 exact architecture smoke 都已完成；主要风险是 routed full heads 会把行为拉回接近 `shared_routed_expert_topk` 而缺乏新的 Pareto 价值，但这本身也是清晰结论。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0129.json:30:        "value": "shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk"
research/history/round_summaries/round_0129.json:38:      "已实际新增并注册 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk`，真实改动仅落在 `sparsify/config.py` 与 `sparsify/sparse_coder.py`。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0129.json:39:      "本地 exact architecture smoke 已通过：`ARCHITECTURE=shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk, K=128, EF=1, FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=256, NUM_EXPERTS=64, ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2, LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=320` 可 instantiate/forward/backward。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0129.json:43:      "如果该点在约 0.37x 下把 FVU 明显拉回到接近 `shared_routed_expert_topk` 低成本前沿，则下一轮保持新 family 不变，只改 `LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=384` 或 `K=112`，定位这条新线的 low-cost knee。",
