research/history/round_summaries/round_0214.json:19:    "hypothesis": "\u5019\u9009 family \u8bbe\u4e3a `lowrank_expert_topk`\u3002\u6700\u7ec8\u91cd\u6784\u516c\u5f0f\u5199\u4e3a `x_hat = \u03a3_r \u03b2_r(x) u_r + \u03a3_{e\u2208E(x)} \u03a3_{i\u2208S_e(x)} \u03b1_{e,i}(x) b_{e,i}`\uff0c\u5176\u4e2d `{u_r}` \u662f\u9759\u6001 low-rank trunk \u5411\u91cf\u5e93\uff0c`{b_{e,i}}` \u662f\u5404 expert \u7684\u9759\u6001\u5b50\u5e93\u539f\u5b50\uff1b\u5728\u7ebf\u4fa7\u5148\u8ba1\u7b97\u5c11\u91cf trunk \u7cfb\u6570\uff0c\u518d\u505a\u8f7b\u91cf router \u9009\u62e9\u5c11\u91cf expert \u5b50\u5e93\uff0c\u5e76\u5728\u6240\u9009\u9759\u6001\u5b50\u5e93\u5185\u505a local top-k\u3001\u67e5\u8868\u3001\u52a0\u6743\u6c42\u548c\uff0c\u6700\u7ec8\u4ecd\u53ef\u76f4\u63a5\u5bfc\u51fa\u5230 LUTurbo/Lottable \u7684\u201ctrunk \u67e5\u8868/\u52a0\u6743\u548c + \u5b50\u5e93\u9009\u62e9 + \u67e5\u8868 + \u52a0\u6743\u6c42\u548c + \u9009\u62e9\u6027\u8865\u507f\u201d\u94fe\u8def\uff0c\u56e0\u6b64 `lowrank_expert_topk` \u5c5e\u4e8e `\u6269\u5c55\u517c\u5bb9`\u3002`expert_topk`\u3001`shared_routed_expert_topk` \u5c5e\u4e8e\u76f4\u63a5\u517c\u5bb9\uff1b`batch_topk`\u3001`adaptive_budget_topk` \u7b49 batch/sample-coupled family \u4ecd\u662f\u4e0d\u517c\u5bb9\uff0c\u4e0d\u80fd\u9a71\u52a8\u5f53\u524d objective leaderboard\u3002\u672c\u8f6e\u552f\u4e00\u4e3b\u5047\u8bbe\u662f\uff1ar212 \u5df2\u628a routed-only `expert_topk` \u538b\u5230 exact total_cost_ratio=0.1640625\uff0c\u4f46 r213 \u4e5f\u8bf4\u660e\u7ee7\u7eed\u628a K \u4ece 32 \u538b\u5230 16 \u4f1a\u4e3b\u8981\u4ee5 exceed \u5931\u63a7\u4e3a\u4ee3\u4ef7\uff0c\u8bf4\u660e\u5f53\u524d incumbent \u5df2\u4e0d\u518d\u5355\u7eaf\u7f3a lookup \u538b\u7f29\uff0c\u800c\u5f00\u59cb\u7f3a\u5c11\u201c\u5e73\u6ed1\u4e3b\u5e72 + sparse residual\u201d\u5f0f\u7684\u8d28\u91cf\u652f\u6491\u3002\u56e0\u6b64\u76f8\u5bf9 r212 \u4ec5\u628a `ARCHITECTURE` \u4ece `expert_topk` \u5207\u5230 `lowrank_expert_topk`\uff0c\u4fdd\u6301 `K=32`\u3001`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`\u3001`TRUNK_RANK=16`\u3001`NUM_EXPERTS=128`\u3001`ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2`\u3001`LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=192`\u3001`FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=256`\u3001`adam`\u3001`LR=8e-4` \u4e0e\u5176\u4f59\u8bad\u7ec3\u914d\u65b9\u4e0d\u53d8\uff0c\u76f4\u63a5\u56de\u7b54\u201c\u5728\u5f53\u524d ultra-small-K \u4e3b\u7ebf\u4e0b\uff0c\u52a0\u4e00\u4e2a\u4fbf\u5b9c\u7684 low-rank trunk \u662f\u5426\u80fd\u7528\u9002\u5ea6 cost \u56de\u5347\u6362\u56de\u8db3\u591f\u591a\u7684 exceed \u4e0b\u964d\u201d\u3002\u672c\u5730\u6210\u672c\u590d\u6838\u663e\u793a\u8be5\u70b9 selection_accesses=557056\u3001deployment_accesses=245760\u3001combined_accesses=802816\uff0c\u5bf9\u5f53\u524d 1024x4096 fused-QKV proxy \u7684 exact total_cost_ratio=0.19140625\uff1b\u76f8\u5bf9 r212 \u7684 exact 0.1640625 \u589e\u52a0\u4e86 0.02734375 \u7684\u6210\u672c\uff0c\u56e0\u6b64\u8981\u5237\u65b0 incumbent\uff0c\u9700\u8981 exceed \u538b\u5230\u7ea6 0.16819375 \u4ee5\u4e0b\u3002\u8fd9\u4e2a\u95e8\u69db\u867d\u7136\u4e0d\u4f4e\uff0c\u4f46\u5e76\u975e\u8131\u79bb\u73b0\u5b9e\uff1a\u5f53\u524d target \u4e0a\u540c family \u7684\u65e7\u70b9 r200 \u5728\u66f4\u5f31\u7684 `NUM_EXPERTS=64`\u3001\u540c `TRUNK_RANK=16`\u3001\u66f4\u9ad8 `K=64` \u4e0b\u5df2\u6709 exceed=0.188017\uff1b\u82e5 doubled expert bank + wider local heads \u80fd\u660e\u663e\u4fee\u590d ultra-small-K \u4e0b\u7684 tail error\uff0c`lowrank_expert_topk` \u662f\u5f53\u524d remaining compatible families \u91cc\u6700\u6709\u5e0c\u671b\u5728 `0.19x` \u4e3b\u6218\u573a\u76f4\u63a5\u56de\u7b54\u8be5\u95ee\u9898\u7684\u7ed3\u6784\u69fd\u4f4d\u3002",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0214.json:44:      "\u5982\u679c\u8be5\u70b9\u4ecd\u660e\u663e\u5f31\u4e8e r212\uff0c\u8bf4\u660e cheap trunk \u4e5f\u4e0d\u8db3\u4ee5\u4fee\u590d\u5f53\u524d ultra-small-K routed-only \u4e3b\u7ebf\u7684 tail error\uff1b\u540e\u7eed\u5e94\u505c\u6b62\u671f\u5f85 trunk-only \u65b9\u6848\u5728\u8fd9\u4e2a cost \u5e26\u5b8c\u6210\u7a81\u7834\uff0c\u8f6c\u5411\u66f4\u660e\u786e\u7684\u4e0d\u5bf9\u79f0 cleanup \u7ed3\u6784\uff0c\u5982 `shared_two_stage_residual_expert` \u4e00\u7c7b\u7684\u65b0 architecture probe\u3002"
research/history/round_summaries/round_0175.json:19:    "hypothesis": "候选 family 保持为 `lowrank_expert_topk`。最终重构公式为 `x_hat = Σ_r β_r(x) u_r + Σ_{e∈E(x)} Σ_{i∈S_e(x)} α_{e,i}(x) b_{e,i}`：其中 `{u_r}` 是静态 low-rank trunk 库，`{b_{e,i}}` 是静态 expert 子库原子；在线侧先计算 trunk 系数与轻量 router，再在少量静态 expert 子库内做局部 top-k，最终仍是静态向量库上的有限加权和，可直接导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“trunk 查表/加权和 + expert 子库查表 + 有限加权和”链路，因此兼容性判断为 `扩展兼容`。`batch_topk`、`adaptive_budget_topk` 这类 batch/sample-coupled family 仍是 `不兼容`，只能保留历史参考，不能驱动当前 frontier。当前 `<0.25x` 主战场里，最近的 architecture-level probes `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk`、`factorized_topk` 已在 matched low-cost recipe 下给出明确负信号，而 `shared_routed_factorized_expert_topk` / `factorized_expert_topk` 也已有更早低成本负信号；相对之下，`lowrank_expert_topk` 仍是唯一在当前 low-cost 带内离现有 anchor 最近、且尚未完成 trunk 压缩定界的兼容 family。相对 r170 只把 `TRUNK_RANK` 从 `16` 降到 `8`，保持 `ARCHITECTURE=lowrank_expert_topk`、`K=96`、`LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=224`、`ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2`、`NUM_EXPERTS=64`、`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`、`adam`、`LR=8e-4` 不变，直接回答“低秩 trunk 是否还能进一步左移到约 0.23x，同时保住足够接近当前 0.23x-0.24x anchors 的质量”。，基于当前成本口径复核，该配置仍位于预期成本带内并满足预算约束。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0175.json:25:    "self_review": "这轮严格遵守 param_only 单变量约束：相对 r170 只改 `TRUNK_RANK`。虽然当前策略偏好 architecture-level probe，但最近两轮已经用 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk` 与 `factorized_topk` 补过新的低成本结构证据，且结果都偏负；继续切向已知低成本负信号更强的 family，信息增量反而更低。选择 `lowrank_expert_topk@TRUNK_RANK=8`，是因为它仍是当前 `<0.25x` 带内最接近现有 anchors 的非主线兼容 family，而 trunk 压缩是尚未完成的高信息量结构轴。主要风险是 rank=8 过薄导致 FVU 明显回退；但若不做这一步，就无法判断这条 family 是否还能在更左的 0.23x 附近保住竞争力。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0175.json:36:      "最近 low-cost architecture probes 已给出更清晰负信号：r172/r174 的 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk` 仍明显弱于同带 anchors，r173 的 `factorized_topk` 更显著落后；当前不应再让这些 family 主导 `<0.25x` 预算。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0175.json:63:    "self_review": "这轮严格遵守 param_only 单变量约束：相对 r170 只改 `TRUNK_RANK`。虽然当前策略偏好 architecture-level probe，但最近两轮已经用 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk` 与 `factorized_topk` 补过新的低成本结构证据，且结果都偏负；继续切向已知低成本负信号更强的 family，信息增量反而更低。选择 `lowrank_expert_topk@TRUNK_RANK=8`，是因为它仍是当前 `<0.25x` 带内最接近现有 anchors 的非主线兼容 family，而 trunk 压缩是尚未完成的高信息量结构轴。主要风险是 rank=8 过薄导致 FVU 明显回退；但若不做这一步，就无法判断这条 family 是否还能在更左的 0.23x 附近保住竞争力。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0139.json:7:  "family_name": "shared_lowrank_routed_expert_residual",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0139.json:20:    "hypothesis": "最终重构公式为 x_hat = Σ_{i∈S_sh(h(x))} α_i^sh(x) u_i + Σ_{j∈S_{e(x)}(x)} α_{e,j}(x) b_{e,j} + Σ_{m∈S_res(x-x_stage1)} γ_m(x) c_m，其中 h(x)=ReLU(Bx)，U={u_i} 是 shared 静态向量库，{B_e} 是 routed expert 静态子库，C={c_m} 是全局 residual 静态库，x_stage1 为 shared+routed stage 的重构。在线导出链路仍是“shared low-rank projection + shared library lookup + 单 expert local top-k + residual library lookup + 有限加权和”，静态库不随样本动态生成，因此该 family 判定为扩展兼容，不是不兼容 family。唯一主假设：相对 r138 仅把 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS` 从 2 降到 1，保持 `ARCHITECTURE=shared_lowrank_routed_expert_residual`、`K=128`、`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`、`FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=192`、`LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=320`、`STAGE1_RATIO=0.25` 与其余训练配方不变，利用 residual cleanup 吃掉少掉的第二个 routed expert 覆盖，从而把 total_cost 从约 0.60x 压到约 0.52x，同时尽量保住 r138 的 FVU=0.0946，回答这条 hetero MoE + residual 线能否在 0.5x 左右形成新的结构性 Pareto 段。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0139.json:21:    "summary": "已实际修复 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_residual` 的参数接线 blocker，使该新 family 后续可以合法做单变量 param-only 探针。建议本轮以 r138 为 reference，只改 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS=1`，直接测试“shared low-rank basis + 单 routed expert + residual cleanup”能否把这条 hetero MoE 线从约 0.60x 压到约 0.52x total_cost，并保持足够接近 r138 的质量。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0139.json:24:    "family_name": "shared_lowrank_routed_expert_residual",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0139.json:26:    "self_review": "先修真实 blocker，再发实验：r138 已证明 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_residual` 有结构价值，但此前它没有接入 family-specific override allowlist，后续任何合法的单变量 param-only 探针都会在训练前被判为 disallowed。当前已实际补上该 wiring，并做了本地 allowlist 自检。计划运行时相对 r138 只改 1 个 env 参数 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS`，满足单变量原则；风险是第二个 routed expert 仍对当前 target 很关键，导致 FVU 回退，但这会直接回答 residual stage 是否足以支撑更轻的 expert 激活路径。",
