research/history/round_summaries/round_0113.json:35:      "截至 round 112，当前工作区真实 frontier 已包含兼容的 `shared_routed_expert_topk` 段：r107 0.42x/0.1010，r108 0.38x/0.1072，r109 0.34x/0.1147，r110 0.32x/0.1191，r111 0.30x/0.1228，r112 0.28x/0.1282。",
