research/history/round_summaries/round_0141.json:36:      "本轮不是回到 `shared_routed_expert_topk` 做旧 family 局部微调，而是以当前低成本 reference r123 为 matched baseline，直接重验更符合当前 agenda 的 hetero MoE 结构 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk`。",
