research/history/logs/agent_action_0293.json:1:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"扩展兼容新结构 probe：`shared_adaptive_active_product_key_expert_residual` 的最终重构为 x_hat = Σ_{i∈S_sh(x)} α_i^sh b_i^sh + Σ_{e∈E_pk^*(r1(x))} Σ_{j∈S_e^τ(r1(x))} α_{e,j} b_{e,j} + Σ_{m∈S_res(r2(x))} γ_m c_m，其中 r1(x)=x-Σ α_i^sh b_i^sh，r2(x)=x-Σ α_i^sh b_i^sh-Σ α_{e,j} b_{e,j}。shared coarse、adaptive PK expert cleanup 与 residual cleanup 都落在静态向量库上，在线侧仍是 LUTurbo/Lottable 可导出的查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿流水线，因此兼容性判定为扩展兼容。主假设是：在 `shared_product_key_expert_residual` 的 cleanup scaffold 上加入 difficulty-aware adaptive-active expert path，能比固定 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2` 更强地降低 hard-token exceed，而 cost proxy 基本不变。","summary":"已实际新增并集成 `shared_adaptive_active_product_key_expert_residual`，只在 `sparsify/` 落盘修改 whitelist 与 runtime dispatch/class implementation。该 family 复用 `shared_product_key_expert_residual` 的 shared + PK + residual scaffold，仅把 expert cleanup 改成 adaptive-active 选择。按本地 smoke 与 cost 估计，在继承 r282 的 `K=32, EF=1, NUM_EXPERTS=2048, ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2, LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=56, STAGE1_RATIO=0.25, FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=256` 配置下 total_cost_ratio 仍约 `0.12x`，与 r288/r292 同量级；这使本轮成为一个纯粹检验“variable-active cleanup 是否能显著压低 exceed”的 matched-cost architecture probe。","change_type":"edit_sae_code","expected_win":"lower_objective","family_name":"shared_adaptive_active_product_key_expert_residual","family_stage":"prototype","self_review":"这是一次有信息增量的新结构 probe，而不是继续扫已平台化的 split 邻域。风险在于 cost proxy 不会奖励 adaptive-active 的轻路径，所以若 exceed 改善不够，这条线可能仍输给 incumbent；但它正面回答了当前最高价值的问题：在保留 shared+PK+residual scaffold 的同时，difficulty-aware cleanup 是否值得继续。","needs_sanity":true,"env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"shared_adaptive_active_product_key_expert_residual"}],"touched_files":["sparsify/config.py","sparsify/sparse_coder.py"],"notes_to_memory":["已落盘新增 family：`shared_adaptive_active_product_key_expert_residual`，并完成 `sparsify/config.py` whitelist 与 `sparsify/sparse_coder.py` dispatch/class 接线。","本地 exact-string smoke 已通过：`shared_adaptive_active_product_key_expert_residual` 在 `K=32, EF=1, NUM_EXPERTS=2048, ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2, LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=56, STAGE1_RATIO=0.25, FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=256` 下可实例化并 forward/backward。","本地 cost 估计：selection_ratio≈0.08，deployment_ratio≈0.04，total_cost_ratio≈0.12；与 `shared_product_key_expert_residual` 同量级，适合作为 matched-cost exceed probe。","该 family 的结构语义是：shared coarse 吃主干，adaptive-active PK experts 按难度做 cleanup，最后 tiny residual head 做全局 tail cleanup；兼容性应视为扩展兼容。"],"next_hypotheses":["若本轮 exceed 明显低于 r288/r292 且 objective 接近或优于 incumbent，再以该 family 为 anchor 做一次最小 knee 校准，例如 `STAGE1_RATIO` 或 residual split。","若本轮 objective 仍无改善，则可将‘adaptive-active + residual cleanup’这条线一并降级，后续应转向真正不同的 coarse/shared 表达方式，而不是继续在 PK cleanup 语义上叠层。","若本轮出现 sanity 或 registration 异常，优先把它当新 family 集成问题处理，并用同一 exact architecture string 重做 smoke/dispatch 检查。"],"reference_round":282}
research/history/round_summaries/round_0300.json:19:    "hypothesis": "\u6700\u7ec8\u91cd\u6784\u516c\u5f0f\u8bbe\u4e3a `x_hat = \u03a3_{i\u2208S_sh(x)} \u03b1_i^sh(x) b_i^sh + \u03a3_{e\u2208E_pk(r1(x))} \u03a3_{j\u2208S_e^\u03c4(r1(x))} \u03b1_{e,j}(x) b_{e,j} + \u03a3_{m\u2208S_res^\u03c4(r2(x))} \u03b3_m(x) c_m`\uff0c\u5176\u4e2d `r1(x)=x-\u03a3_i \u03b1_i^sh(x) b_i^sh`\uff0c`r2(x)=r1(x)-\u03a3_{e,j} \u03b1_{e,j}(x) b_{e,j}`\uff1b`{b_i^sh}` \u662f always-on shared coarse \u9759\u6001\u5b50\u5e93\uff0c`{b_{e,j}}` \u662f product-key \u8def\u7531\u5230\u7684\u9759\u6001 expert \u5b50\u5e93\uff0c`{c_m}` \u662f tiny residual \u9759\u6001\u5b50\u5e93\uff0c\u800c\u6700\u540e\u4e00\u6bb5 residual \u7cfb\u6570 `\u03b3_m(x)` \u4f7f\u7528 JumpReLU-gated residual scorer\u3002\u5bfc\u51fa\u5230 LUTurbo/Lottable \u65f6\uff0c\u5728\u7ebf\u94fe\u8def\u4ecd\u662f\u201cshared \u67e5\u8868 -> PK expert \u5b50\u5e93\u67e5\u8868 -> JumpReLU residual \u5b50\u5e93\u67e5\u8868 -> \u6709\u9650\u52a0\u6743\u548c -> \u9009\u62e9\u6027\u5728\u7ebf\u8865\u507f\u201d\uff0c\u4e0d\u6d89\u53ca\u52a8\u6001\u5b57\u5178\u751f\u6210\uff0c\u56e0\u6b64\u8be5 family \u5224\u5b9a\u4e3a `\u6269\u5c55\u517c\u5bb9`\u3002`shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu`\u3001`product_key_expert_jumprelu`\u3001`dual_shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu` \u7b49\u517c\u5bb9 family \u4ecd\u53ef\u53c2\u4e0e\u5f53\u524d objective leaderboard\uff1b`batch_topk`\u3001`adaptive_budget_topk` \u7b49\u4e0d\u517c\u5bb9 family \u53ea\u80fd\u4f5c\u4e3a\u5386\u53f2\u53c2\u8003\uff0c\u4e0d\u80fd\u9a71\u52a8\u540e\u7eed\u51b3\u7b56\u3002\u672c\u8f6e\u552f\u4e00\u4e3b\u5047\u8bbe\u662f\uff1a\u5728\u8fde\u7eed\u4e24\u8f6e `NUM_EXPERTS` \u6269\u5bb9\u5df2\u663e\u793a 3072 \u6709\u9650\u6b63\u4fe1\u53f7\u30014096 \u660e\u663e\u56de\u64a4\u4e4b\u540e\uff0c\u5f53\u524d low-K \u4e3b\u74f6\u9888\u66f4\u50cf\u662f hard-token tail cleanup \u8bed\u4e49\uff0c\u800c\u4e0d\u662f\u7ee7\u7eed\u6269 routed bank \u7c92\u5ea6\uff1b\u56e0\u6b64\u5e94\u5207\u6362\u7ed3\u6784\u69fd\u4f4d\uff0c\u800c\u4e0d\u662f\u7ee7\u7eed\u5728 incumbent family \u4e0a\u505a\u8fd1\u90bb\u63d2\u503c\u3002\u76f8\u5bf9 r282 \u53ea\u6539 `ARCHITECTURE=shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu_residual`\uff0c\u5176\u4f59 `K=32`\u3001`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`\u3001`NUM_EXPERTS=2048`\u3001`ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2`\u3001`LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=56`\u3001`STAGE1_RATIO=0.25`\u3001`OPTIMIZER=adam`\u3001`LR=8e-4` \u4fdd\u6301\u4e0d\u53d8\uff0c\u76f4\u63a5\u6d4b\u8bd5\u201c\u5728 winning shared+PK scaffold \u4e0a\uff0c\u628a\u6700\u7ec8 tiny residual cleanup \u4ece plain residual \u8bed\u4e49\u6362\u6210 JumpReLU-gated tail cleanup\u201d\u80fd\u5426\u66f4\u6709\u6548\u538b\u4f4e `exceed_alpha_0.50`\u3002\u672c\u5730\u7cbe\u786e\u6210\u672c\u81ea\u68c0\u663e\u793a\u8be5\u70b9 `selection_accesses=325696`\u3001`deployment_accesses=163840`\u3001`combined_accesses=489536`\u3001`exact total_cost_ratio=0.1167144775390625`\uff0c\u6ee1\u8db3\u9884\u7b97\uff1b\u82e5\u8981\u51fb\u8d25\u5f53\u524d incumbent `objective=0.2684179902076721`\uff0c\u9700\u8981\u628a `exceed_alpha_0.50` \u538b\u5230 `0.1517035126686096` \u4ee5\u4e0b\u3002",
